These are Puzzles for 1x2 Level 8

.:: Puzzle 1x2-Level-8-1::.
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: reggae, folk
1. the fan of reggae is on the right of the fan of folk##1
2. the fan of folk is not to the right of the fan of folk##8

.:: Answer ::.
|               |  1   |  2  |
| Music-Genre   | folk | reggae |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x2-Level-8-2::.
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: disaster, zombie
1. the person watching disaster movies is on the far right##1
2. the person watching disaster movies is not to the left of the person watching zombie movies##8

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2    |
| Movie-Genre   | zombie | disaster |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x2-Level-8-3::.
2 different pets are kept: guinea-pig, chinchilla
1. the owner of the guinea-pig is somewhere to the left of the owner of the chinchilla##5
2. the owner of the chinchilla is on the left or right of the owner of the guinea-pig##3
3. the owner of the guinea-pig is not to the right of the owner of the guinea-pig##8

.:: Answer ::.
|       |    1     |    2     |
| Pet   | guinea-pig | chinchilla |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x2-Level-8-4::.
The people use 2 different means of transport: bike, motorbike
1. the person driving the bike is not to the right of the person driving the bike##8
2. the person driving the motorbike is on the right of the person driving the bike##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1    |   2   |
| Transport   | bike | motorbike |

 #################################

 
